Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.42,0:00:38.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}在遙遠的北方{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.18,0:00:41.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}經過三個月暗無天日的冬季後{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.50,0:00:49.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}有個世界正在等待著{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.66,0:00:54.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}一個契機{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.18,0:00:59.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}春天的陽光{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.42,0:01:14.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}海星是第一個對陽光產生反應的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.50,0:01:29.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}它們爭相朝著最高點爬去{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.86,0:01:34.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}它們的管足尖{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.38,0:01:36.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}感覺到海水裏的變化{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.34,0:01:40.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}於是它們便開始產卵{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.82,0:01:58.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}海參{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.10,0:02:00.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}原本只露出個口部{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.54,0:02:02.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}現在它也現出了全身{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.70,0:02:15.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}它們要盡量多收集些海星卵{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.82,0:02:34.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}當你有十隻觸手時 收集的海星卵數量是相當可觀的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.38,0:02:48.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}現在海鰓也要冒出來分一杯羹{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.26,0:03:03.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}這裏的動物們必須要盡量從這一年一度的盛宴中多撈些好處{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.30,0:03:13.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}因為陽光出現時 一場規模浩大的變化也將隨之而來{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.94,0:03:20.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}海藻是一種海生澡類 大量的海藻{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.38,0:03:22.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}因氣囊內充滿了氣體{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.34,0:03:25.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}漸漸朝海面上升{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.14,0:03:41.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}很快 一座海底森林就誕生了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.42,0:03:48.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}裏頭住滿了各種各樣的生物{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.26,0:03:57.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}這些綠色海洋的物產 雖然在世界上是首屈一指的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.46,0:04:00.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}但是這裏也是{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.14,0:04:01.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}競爭最為激烈的水域{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.36,0:04:13.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}綠色海洋{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.62,0:04:21.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}非洲的南端{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.66,0:04:27.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}兩個大洋在這裏衝撞{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.50,0:04:43.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}在淺水區 營養豐富的水流滋養著{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.30,0:04:46.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}茂盛的海藻森林{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.66,0:05:02.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}這裏頭幾乎什麼也看不見 只能看到一個虹吸管在有規律地跳動{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.90,0:05:06.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}它就是靠虹吸管來呼吸的 一隻普通章魚{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.66,0:05:08.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}正在等著獵物經過{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.94,0:05:16.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}就是這只螃蟹了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.54,0:05:25.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}章魚動身追蹤螃蟹{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.38,0:05:58.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}然後潛伏起來{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.30,0:06:03.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}耐心等待 準備伏擊{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.34,0:06:31.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}不過章魚是和大量其他捕食性動物{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.42,0:06:34.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}共同生活在好望角水域裏的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.86,0:06:44.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}海狗{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.66,0:06:47.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}還有鯊魚{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.86,0:06:52.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}它們全是吃章魚的動物{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.26,0:06:56.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}前提是它們能找到章魚{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.82,0:07:07.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}睡袍鯊是下層叢林的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.46,0:07:12.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}獵捕專家{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.02,0:07:21.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}是時候消失了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.02,0:07:31.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}不過這些皮糙肉厚的小鯊魚{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.26,0:07:35.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}小到能夠觸達裂隙深處{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.98,0:07:57.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}不過章魚離死還遠著呢{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.74,0:08:03.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}它把腕溜進了鯊魚的鰓裏{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.02,0:08:07.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}這樣鯊魚就無法呼吸{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.42,0:08:14.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}鯊魚只好放它離開{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.74,0:08:28.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}這只章魚在外頭的危險地帶時{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.78,0:08:32.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}它會做一件讓人意想不到的事情{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.10,0:08:36.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}而這件事情是我們從未記載過的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.26,0:08:49.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}它用一堆貝殼{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.90,0:08:54.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}做了個防護器具用來掩蔽自己{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.58,0:09:03.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}它就躲在敵人的眼皮子底下{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.22,0:09:17.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}鯊魚能夠聞到章魚的氣味{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.38,0:09:32.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}但是貝殼卻把鯊魚給搞糊塗了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.34,0:09:41.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}在這個隨處可見捕食性動物的森林裏{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.82,0:09:46.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}這只章魚就是靠著高人一等的才智生存下來的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.94,0:10:03.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}海藻森林主要是在世界各地的季節性水域裏繁榮生長{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.90,0:10:11.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}特別是北美洲的太平洋沿岸{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.62,0:10:22.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}在這裏 世界上最大的海藻{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.30,0:10:24.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}在廣袤的森林裏生長著{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.26,0:10:27.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}它們可延伸至幾百千米外的位置{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.34,0:10:35.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}在某些地方 這些巨大的植物體{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.58,0:10:38.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}甚至高達60米{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.54,0:10:48.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}這些海藻形成的植叢裏密佈著各種生物{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.62,0:11:01.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}這裏的生存空間和食物競爭非常激烈{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.46,0:11:18.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}這對這只美國紅雀鯛來說是一大挑戰{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.22,0:11:28.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}它精心照料著自己的海藻地盤{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.18,0:11:31.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}裏頭的小動物全是它的食物{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.02,0:11:44.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}和大多數農民一樣 它也是一天到晚忙個不停{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.30,0:11:52.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}有些蝸牛和食草動物會來吃它的海藻{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.38,0:11:54.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}它就把這些動物給弄出去{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.22,0:12:15.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}不管它們的體型有多大{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.58,0:12:29.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}它還得對付各種各樣的有害生物{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.14,0:12:34.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}這只動物帶來的後果可能是最嚴重的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.62,0:12:39.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}海膽會把岩石上的海藻全都刮下來{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.94,0:12:43.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}它的刺毛和針一樣鋒利{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.26,0:12:48.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}這只雀鯛一定要想方設法把它弄走{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.02,0:13:05.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}但問題是海膽的數量{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.62,0:13:13.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}變得越來越多{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.30,0:13:33.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}等夜幕降臨 光線變弱時 它就得收手了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.30,0:13:37.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}它不僅需要休息 它還需要躲起來{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.38,0:13:46.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}因為在夜間 捕食動物會在這些森林裏穿梭覓食{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.30,0:13:52.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}電鰩{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.34,0:13:57.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}能用45伏的電壓把獵物電暈{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.02,0:14:10.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}雀鯛躲起來時{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.58,0:14:15.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}海膽們就能夠肆無忌憚地吃海藻了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.98,0:14:27.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}陽光再次照進海裏{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.98,0:14:34.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}它發現自己的農田又遭到了破壞{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.14,0:14:53.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}海膽和蝗蟲一樣{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.26,0:14:56.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}往往蜂擁而至{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.06,0:15:06.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}這會帶來災難性的後果 損失慘重的不僅僅是雀鯛{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.98,0:15:10.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}還有海藻森林本身{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.46,0:15:26.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}所有植物現在都遭到了破壞{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.54,0:15:57.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}海膽在森林中四處游動{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.42,0:16:00.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}穿過海藻田{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.10,0:16:02.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}留下的卻是大片的不毛之地{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.02,0:16:10.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}北美洲太平洋沿岸的許多海藻森林{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.46,0:16:13.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}都被這些成群出沒的海膽糟蹋了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.26,0:16:22.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}不過好在幫手就在附近{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.74,0:16:44.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}海獺{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.90,0:16:53.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}其他水獺大多是在陸地上生活{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.70,0:16:56.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}只有海獺常年生活在水裏{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.38,0:17:04.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}剛出生的小海獺還不太會游泳{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.90,0:17:09.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}為了能讓它浮起來 它的母親花了好幾個小時幫它理毛{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.38,0:17:20.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}不過為了能讓孩子吃到母乳 並為自己保暖{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.58,0:17:24.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}它每天吃的食物重量必須達到自身體重的30％才行{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.06,0:17:47.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}它主要是靠水生有殼動物來增重{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.34,0:17:56.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}海膽就是海獺最喜歡吃的美食之一{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.50,0:18:20.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}在過去 人們為了得到海獺的毛皮 大量獵殺海獺{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.10,0:18:22.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}海獺幾乎瀕臨滅絕{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.14,0:18:33.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}海獺的數量減少後 很多海藻森林都被海膽破壞得寸草不生{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.30,0:18:46.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}如今海獺得到了保護{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.50,0:18:52.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}隨著海獺的數量逐漸回升{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.18,0:18:55.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}很多海藻森林也慢慢恢復了原貌{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.74,0:19:13.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}如今 某些僻遠地帶{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.62,0:19:15.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}生活著大量的海獺{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.46,0:19:19.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}它們總是成群地聚在一起{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.14,0:19:27.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}我們已經有100多年沒見到這一情形了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.30,0:20:12.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}在澳洲陽光充沛的淺水區裏生長的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.06,0:20:19.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}不是海藻 而是海洋裏唯一的開花植物{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.14,0:20:21.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}海草{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.10,0:20:32.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}在這些海洋草地中 最廣闊的草地{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.78,0:20:36.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}面積可達到八千多平方千米{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.14,0:20:54.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}整個熱帶地區的海洋草地 都是由鼬鯊巡邏著{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.82,0:21:01.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}鼬鯊的身體可長至五米{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.30,0:21:10.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}它們那有力的雙顎能讓獵物皮開肉綻{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.78,0:21:22.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}它們的獵物是綠海龜{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.26,0:21:31.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}綠海龜幾乎完全以海草為食{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.22,0:21:38.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}一隻綠海龜每天食用的海草就多達兩公斤{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.90,0:21:56.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}不過它們始終不能放鬆警惕{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.26,0:22:11.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}健康的綠海龜要與不斷逼近的鯊魚保持一定的距離{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.14,0:22:29.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}鯊魚在迫使綠海龜逃離的同時{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.78,0:22:34.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}也避免了海草地遭到過度啃噬{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.86,0:22:43.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}這對我們大家都有好處{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.02,0:22:55.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}與同面積的熱帶雨林相比{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.30,0:22:58.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}海草地吸收並儲存的二氧化碳量{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.90,0:23:02.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}是前者的35倍{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.58,0:23:11.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}因此在這場對抗氣候變暖的戰役中 草地和鯊魚{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.82,0:23:14.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}竟然是同一陣營的盟友{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.30,0:23:27.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}綠色海洋裏艱難的生存環境{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.18,0:23:29.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}可能會帶來深遠的影響{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.06,0:23:38.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}每年 澳洲的一塊草地會發生變化{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.38,0:23:48.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}在冬季的首個滿月日子前後{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.90,0:23:51.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}一支軍隊形成了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.74,0:23:56.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}蜘蛛蟹{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.58,0:24:07.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}過去一年 它們一直在深海區裏覓食{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.26,0:24:22.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}現在它們要穿過海草平原{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.78,0:24:43.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}數以十萬計的蜘蛛蟹{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.94,0:24:53.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}它們爬到彼此身上{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.26,0:25:02.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}形成了巨大的山丘{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.26,0:25:10.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}綿延近百米{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.34,0:25:18.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}它們並不是在求偶 也不是在產卵{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.98,0:25:21.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}它們來到這裏是為了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.90,0:25:23.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}長大{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.82,0:25:27.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}和所有的螃蟹一樣{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.30,0:25:29.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}它們的身體也是包裹在堅硬{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.06,0:25:31.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}不具伸縮性的殼內{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.46,0:25:37.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}因此為了長大 它們必須要破殼而出{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.78,0:25:53.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}這樣硬殼底下發育的軟殼就能夠逐漸變大{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.42,0:26:04.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}新殼要花上好幾天時間才能變硬{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:16.62,0:26:20.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}它們的腿瘸得很厲害 所以現在還無法自如行動{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:24.38,0:26:28.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}失去保護的蜘蛛蟹處境非常危險{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:37.46,0:26:39.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}短尾刺魟{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:42.90,0:26:45.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}它的體型很大 體長將近達到四米{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:47.86,0:26:51.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}它想要抓只剛換殼的軟嫩蜘蛛蟹嘗嘗{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:51.66,0:26:53.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}這樣的蜘蛛蟹吃起來更省事{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:15.02,0:27:17.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}蜘蛛蟹們想要聚在一起{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:25.38,0:27:27.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}但是經刺魟一攪和{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:27.86,0:27:29.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}蜘蛛蟹們便四處散開了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:35.26,0:27:37.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}剛換殼的蜘蛛蟹{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:37.50,0:27:40.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}還很虛弱 無法跟上隊伍{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:55.22,0:27:58.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}最安全的位置就是蟹群的中央{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:00.58,0:28:03.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}這也是它們全聚到這裏的原因{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:12.26,0:28:14.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}蜘蛛蟹越多的地方也就越安全{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:30.58,0:28:33.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}不過大多數蜘蛛蟹都逃走了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:34.46,0:28:36.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}在接下來的幾天內{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:36.18,0:28:39.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}它們就要準備回到深海裏{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:39.02,0:28:43.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}繼續孤單地漫遊 尋找食物{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:55.22,0:28:57.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}這不是墓地{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:00.18,0:29:05.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}而是十萬隻蜘蛛蟹在這裏成功脫下了殼{\r}
