Dialogue: 0,0:33:23.86,0:33:27.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}小個兒雄烏賊和雌烏賊一樣{\r}
