Dialogue: 0,0:33:37.18,0:33:39.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}它溜到雌烏賊的旁邊{\r}
