Dialogue: 0,0:33:54.54,0:33:57.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}和好幾隻雄烏賊交配{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:59.10,0:34:03.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}雌烏賊便能確保後代基因的多樣性{\r}
