Dialogue: 0,0:34:39.14,0:34:43.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}在澳洲這些綠油油的草地裏{\r}
