Dialogue: 0,0:37:53.94,0:37:57.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}草海龍父親們回到海藻密植叢中{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:57.02,0:37:59.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}在密植叢中它們幾乎沒辦法被發現{\r}
