Dialogue: 0,0:40:25.66,0:40:29.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}小魚只能被迫離開它們的庇護所{\r}
