Dialogue: 0,0:42:22.14,0:42:25.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}雌蝦蛄要靠雄蝦蛄替它尋找食物{\r}
