Dialogue: 0,0:43:18.14,0:43:20.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}它可能會挨餓{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:28.14,0:43:31.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}某樣東西吸引了這只雄蝦蛄的注意力{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:33.86,0:43:36.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}也許是誘人的氣味{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:38.22,0:43:40.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}或許是遠處的呼喚{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:42.90,0:43:44.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}不管是什麼原因{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:44.54,0:43:47.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}雄蝦蛄都準備離開自己的洞穴{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:47.42,0:43:50.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}離開自己的終身伴侶{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:58.46,0:44:01.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}一個更大的洞{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:13.02,0:44:15.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}失去雄性伴侶的雌蝦蛄{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:15.14,0:44:19.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}似乎是在發出求助信號 召喚新的雄性伴侶{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:26.10,0:44:29.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}雌蝦蛄的體型越大 產的卵也就越多{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:29.58,0:44:33.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}所以雄蝦蛄和它交配的話 就能得到更多的後代{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:38.78,0:44:42.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}不過不忠行為是要付出代價的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:45.86,0:44:49.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}伴侶體型越大 食量也就越大{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:45:03.18,0:45:07.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}海洋中生物越豐饒 競爭也就越激烈{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:45:08.50,0:45:10.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}這兒就有個綠色海洋{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:45:10.70,0:45:15.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}它所滋養的生物數量超過了其他所有綠色海洋的總和{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:45:18.02,0:45:21.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}不同於紅樹林和海草草原{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:45:21.26,0:45:24.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}這個綠色海洋位於遠海{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:45:24.50,0:45:28.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}但它只是暫時存在 而且變化莫測{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:45:32.54,0:45:36.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}這些綠色不是生根植物的顏色{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:45:38.66,0:45:41.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}而是一團團懸浮物的顏色{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:45:51.58,0:45:56.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}數十億個微小的浮游植物正在迅速生長{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:46:01.54,0:46:07.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}浮游植物讓這裏本就豐富的食物變成了世界上數一數二的盛宴{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:46:16.90,0:46:19.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}在美洲太平洋海上{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:46:19.62,0:46:24.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}成百上千隻海豚正在匆匆趕去赴宴{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:46:33.82,0:46:36.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}赴宴的不只是它們{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:46:38.90,0:46:40.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}還有海獅{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:46:46.70,0:46:50.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}它們是要前往加州蒙特雷灣{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:46:50.90,0:46:55.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}大量的海藻在那裏繁殖生長{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:46:55.14,0:46:57.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}引來了無數的浮游生物食用者{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:47:00.22,0:47:03.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}數百萬隻鯷魚{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:47:10.34,0:47:13.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}海豚將鯷魚朝著海面逼去{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:47:16.94,0:47:21.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}這些魚群在海面出現後 海鳥和海獅便趁機佔便宜{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:47:26.06,0:47:29.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}它們要趁其他動物到來之前搶先分一杯羹{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:47:49.38,0:47:51.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}座頭鯨{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:47:51.90,0:47:54.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}成百上千頭{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:48:04.14,0:48:06.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}它們每朝上方猛撲一次{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:48:06.30,0:48:09.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}就往肚子裏吞進達100公斤的魚{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:48:26.82,0:48:28.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}在這場地球上罕見的盛宴上{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:48:28.86,0:48:32.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}它們食用的魚量也是最多的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:49:01.90,0:49:04.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}這些微小的浮游生物是如此重要{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:49:04.74,0:49:08.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}幾乎所有的海洋生物最終都要依賴它們才能存活下去{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:49:19.22,0:49:22.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}在世界各地 幾乎所有海洋生物{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:49:24.54,0:49:29.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}都要靠綠色海洋才能生存下去 而不是靠藍色海洋{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:50:03.64,0:50:10.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}幕後集錦{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:50:18.66,0:50:21.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}為了拍攝到海底森林的壯觀景象{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:50:21.58,0:50:25.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}和生活在這裏的神奇生物 《藍色星球》團隊{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:50:25.86,0:50:29.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}研製出了一系列專業攝影設備{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:50:36.30,0:50:40.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}巨型球形攝像機 是在塔狀冠層上{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:50:40.74,0:50:42.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}同時拍攝海上和海裏的畫面{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:50:45.42,0:50:48.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}兩架最先進的延時攝影設備{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:50:48.26,0:50:52.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}用於加快畫面的時間 以揭示林地地表不為人知的景象{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:51:12.34,0:51:15.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}不過在森林裏生活的所有動物中{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:51:15.10,0:51:18.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}南非好望角水域裏的動物{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:51:18.46,0:51:20.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}是拍攝起來最具挑戰性的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:51:23.58,0:51:27.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}博物學家克雷格福斯特對這裏最神秘的居民{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:51:27.10,0:51:31.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}產生了濃厚的興趣 它就是普通章魚{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:51:37.38,0:51:40.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}這些水域裏生活著將近100種鯊魚{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:51:40.98,0:51:42.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}但這並沒有把克雷格嚇倒{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:51:42.94,0:51:46.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}過去六年來 他每天早晨都會游到這裏{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:51:54.06,0:51:57.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}如果你在上面發現了橢圓形小坑{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:51:57.74,0:52:00.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}那你就知道它是被章魚殺死的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:52:01.94,0:52:04.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}你要是再仔細看的話{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:52:04.02,0:52:07.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}那些章魚通常就在這附近{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:52:14.70,0:52:17.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}克雷格親眼見過這些章魚的古怪行徑{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:52:17.86,0:52:21.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}他讓本節目的攝影師羅傑霍洛克斯{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:52:21.14,0:52:23.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}一起看看自己的大發現{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:52:32.22,0:52:36.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}這些動物的性格魅力當即就把羅傑迷住了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:52:38.98,0:52:43.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}普通章魚的個性竟然會是這麼多樣 親眼看到這一幕真的是太讓人吃驚了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:52:43.34,0:52:46.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}普通章魚全都展現出了不同的習性{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:52:48.66,0:52:50.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}有些章魚極其害羞{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:52:50.38,0:52:52.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}有些的膽子非常大{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:52:52.46,0:52:55.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}它們各有各的特性 這也是我喜愛它們的原因{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:53:01.42,0:53:03.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}他們花了數周時間拍攝不同的章魚{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:53:03.98,0:53:05.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}最後它們終於遇上了一隻特別的章魚{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:53:05.90,0:53:09.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}這只章魚看上去不僅不害怕攝像機{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:53:09.10,0:53:11.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}還願為鏡頭表演一番{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:53:21.18,0:53:23.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}它就是這樣冒出來{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:53:23.18,0:53:25.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}接著它就朝著三腳架底下游過去{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:53:25.34,0:53:26.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}游到我的腿旁{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:53:26.74,0:53:28.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}感覺很棒 真的很神奇{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:53:28.86,0:53:32.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}它很快就習慣了我們兩個人{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:53:32.98,0:53:35.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}所以我們拍攝到了那些非常私密的行為{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:53:35.78,0:53:37.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}真是太棒了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:53:41.70,0:53:43.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}我已經觀察這只章魚好幾個月了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:53:43.70,0:53:45.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}我們在海裏時 它很信任我們{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:53:45.30,0:53:48.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}它的行為舉止就跟平時一樣 感覺真的很棒{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:53:56.78,0:54:01.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}幾個月後 它們總算拍攝到了這只明星章魚捕獵的畫面{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:54:18.14,0:54:22.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}但是後來他們也發現了和這麼多捕食性動物{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:54:22.10,0:54:24.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}也就是睡袍鯊同住在一個森林裏{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:54:24.98,0:54:26.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}是要面臨嚴重的後果的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:54:28.06,0:54:30.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}以同等重量比例來說 這些鯊魚比大白鯊{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:54:30.82,0:54:32.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}更加肆無忌憚 更具攻擊性{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:54:32.66,0:54:34.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}它們就像是追蹤導彈{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:54:34.82,0:54:39.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}哪怕章魚只是散發出一點氣味 睡袍鯊都會找到它{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:54:44.30,0:54:46.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}睡袍鯊真的把章魚抓住了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:54:46.98,0:54:49.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}我當時就想這下完了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:54:52.90,0:54:55.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}我和這只動物相處了這麼久{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:54:55.54,0:54:58.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}眼看著它被鯊魚攻擊 我心裏真的很難受{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:55:05.98,0:55:08.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}但是大家都沒想到的是 它反擊了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:55:14.18,0:55:15.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}它把觸手放了下來{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:55:15.90,0:55:18.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}你可以看到那些觸手伸進了鰓裏{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:55:18.18,0:55:20.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}幾乎把鯊魚嘴完全堵住了 鯊魚沒法呼吸{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:55:20.46,0:55:22.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}這樣它就逃走了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:55:22.74,0:55:25.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}這整個過程{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:55:25.58,0:55:29.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}真的是讓人看得心驚肉跳{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:55:30.50,0:55:33.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}章魚逃脫後 團隊成員們都鬆了口氣{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:55:46.02,0:55:48.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}但是當它處在開闊地帶時{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:55:48.30,0:55:51.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}它的另一個花招讓大家更為吃驚{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:55:54.86,0:55:57.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}它把腕舉到頭上{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:55:57.90,0:56:01.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}在這同時 它用腕拉著貝殼材料{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:56:01.46,0:56:04.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}造了個令人難以置信的盔甲{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:56:06.38,0:56:09.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}章魚全副武裝地坐著 接著那傢伙{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:56:09.22,0:56:12.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}從背後游過來 它好像是聞到了章魚的氣味{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:56:12.38,0:56:14.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}但是在它眼前的又不是章魚{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:56:14.34,0:56:17.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}而是那個奇怪的盔甲{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:56:17.66,0:56:20.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}接著它開始撞章魚{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:56:20.10,0:56:23.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}章魚竟然利用那副盔甲 利用知識{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:56:23.14,0:56:25.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}靠自己的計謀戰勝了鯊魚{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:56:25.34,0:56:27.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}這一幕真的是太不可思議了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:56:27.42,0:56:30.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}這絕對是驚人的場景{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:56:35.46,0:56:38.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}它就是個搖滾明星 一個名副其實的小搖滾明星{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:56:40.02,0:56:42.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}多虧了克雷袼和羅傑的貢獻{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:56:42.34,0:56:47.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}現在科學界可以瞭解章魚的驚人之舉了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:56:49.34,0:56:52.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}我們繼續探索這些神奇的地下森林{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:56:52.78,0:56:56.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}還會發現什麼呢{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:57:01.46,0:57:04.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}下期節目{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:57:04.26,0:57:07.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}我們見到的動物是生活在兩個世界碰撞的地帶{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:57:10.26,0:57:12.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}我們將看看它們會如何應對{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:57:12.74,0:57:15.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}變化莫測的海岸環境{\r}

